%%sql
--DROP TABLE ldw.DELTA_VENDAS;
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS ldw.DELTA_VENDAS(
	MERGEKEY CHAR(64),
    NUM_VENDA int,
	DATA_VENDA STRING ,
	ID_CLIENTE int,
	STATUS STRING,
	ID_VENDEDOR int,
	NUM_SEQ int,
	ID_PROD int,
	QTDE DECIMAL(10,2),
	VAL_UNIT DECIMAL(10,2),
	VAL_TOTAL DECIMAL(10,2) ,
	DATA_VENDA_CHAVE STRING,
	ANO STRING,
	MES STRING ,
	CurrentRecord INT,
    EndDate DATE
)
USING DELTA
LOCATION 'abfss://treinamento@adlstrnsolar.dfs.core.windows.net/gold/delta_vendas/'

%%sql
    SELECT ORIGEM.*
    FROM ldw.Original_vendas AS ORIGEM
    WHERE  ORIGEM.MERGEKEY NOT IN (SELECT DELTA.MERGEKEY FROM ldw.DELTA_VENDAS AS DELTA )

%%sql
--Ajuste merge
MERGE INTO ldw.DELTA_VENDAS ALVO
USING (
	
	SELECT ORIGEM.*
    FROM ldw.Original_vendas AS ORIGEM
    WHERE  ORIGEM.MERGEKEY NOT IN (SELECT DELTA.MERGEKEY FROM ldw.DELTA_VENDAS AS DELTA )

	
) P1 --Parte 1
ON ALVO.MERGEKEY = P1.MERGEKEY
WHEN MATCHED THEN
   UPDATE SET ALVO.CurrentRecord = 0, ALVO.EndDate = (CURRENT_DATE)
WHEN NOT MATCHED THEN
  INSERT (
        MERGEKEY,
        NUM_VENDA,
	    DATA_VENDA ,
      	ID_CLIENTE,
      	STATUS,
      	ID_VENDEDOR,
      	NUM_SEQ,
      	ID_PROD,
      	QTDE,
      	VAL_UNIT,
      	VAL_TOTAL ,
      	DATA_VENDA_CHAVE,
      	ANO,
      	MES,
      	CurrentRecord,
            EndDate
  ) VALUES (
            P1.MERGEKEY,
            P1.NUM_VENDA,
	      	P1.DATA_VENDA,
      		P1.ID_CLIENTE,
      		P1.STATUS,
      		P1.ID_VENDEDOR,
      		P1.NUM_SEQ,
      		P1.ID_PROD,
      		P1.QTDE,
      		P1.VAL_UNIT,
      		P1.VAL_TOTAL ,
      		P1.DATA_VENDA_CHAVE,
      		P1.ANO,
      		P1.MES,
      	1, --CURRENT_DATE
